According to the ancient Greek poet Hesiod, Atlas stood at the ends of the earth in extreme west.

metadata.title: Dekion: Self Portrait
metadata.description:
This was made under the influence in a semi-trance state, I can't recall which software I used, it might have been an online drawing tool, it was quite some time ago. 

I awoke and found this image on image on my desktop and instantly loved it. For me, it represents duality. You can clearly see the beautiful angelic with the gruff looking monster hidden inside.

Like I say, this image was a complete accident created in a few seconds with a quick 'swoosh' of my hand but I think it's captured something powerful and intriguing.
